longBusinessSummary: Healthy Extracts Inc., through its subsidiaries, researches, develops, and markets natural plant-based formulations in the United States and internationally. It offers heart health nutritional products; and neuro-products under the KETONOMICS name that enhance brain health, including memory, cognition, focus, and neuro-energy. The company also provides bergamot products in capsule form under the BergaMet Pro+, BergaMet Mega+O, BergaMet HERHEART, BergaMet Cholesterol Command, and BergaMet SPORTSHEART products labels. It distributes bergamot products through its website and distribution sites. The company was formerly known as Grey Cloak Tech Inc. and changed its name to Healthy Extracts Inc. in October 2020. Healthy Extracts Inc. was incorporated in 2014 and is based in Las Vegas, Nevada.
